@startuml stm_primary
title <<stm>> CLight Primary State Machine
skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor<<browse>> #e3f2fd
    BorderColor<<browse>> #1565c0
    FontColor<<browse>> #0d47a1
    BackgroundColor<<terminal>> #e8f5e9
    BorderColor<<terminal>> #2e7d32
}
skinparam shadowing false
top to bottom direction

state "pre_construct" as Pre <<browse>>
state "active" as Active <<browse>>
state "destroyed" as Dead <<terminal>>

Pre -down-> Active : construct\n[ZeroMemory D3DLIGHT8; Type = D3DLIGHT_DIRECTIONAL]
Active --> Active : set_position(V) [-> Direction.xyz]\nset_diffuse_color(C) [-> Diffuse.rgb]\nget_position(_) / get_diffuse_color(_)
Active -down-> Dead : destruct

note right of Active
    Multi-inheritance from D3DLIGHT8.
    NOT observable (no GetChangeEvent).
    "position" maps to D3DLIGHT8::Direction
    -- misleading naming preserved.
end note
@enduml
